# Teravox

Teravox is a custom C-based 3D world editor and rendering engine.

## Features Planned
- ECS architecture
- Scene hierarchy editor
- Gizmo manipulation
- Primitive mesh generation
- Scene serialization
- Audio system
- Real-time renderer
- Object inspector
- Selection system

## Tech
- C
- SDL2
- cimgui
- miniaudio

## Goal
To build a fully custom lightweight 3D world editor from scratch.